name: LR-pov doggy assist
description:
LR-pov doggy assist

Generally speaking, I don't do the work of reinventing the wheel but...Some wheels don't quite meet my requirements, so I have to meet my own needs.

So, this molde just for several scene of pov doggy style:

  • Grabbing arm/ass/torso from behind

  • Looking back

  • Deep penetration (to the base at least)

These are some seemingly simple requirements that cost me a lot of work.

And fanally I got 3 useful versions:

  • V1.0: Gotta simple and even crude frams, but very seldom generates mosaics.

  • V1.1:More delicate scenes and characters.

  • V1.2:Compared to 1.1, details are better portrayed, but loyalty to cue words is lower

Well, they're all common lora, just use as usual, 0.5~0.8 weights.

I was going to add some x-ray view but my rest time is over, so maybe in the future.

## byproduct from failed model, but it's not bad, isn't it? ##
